{"tid":2224858,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北京車展女子維權被蒙黑布抬走","createTime":"2020-10-01T01:05:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T03:22:25.000Z","uid":49776,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"edcdeeda20ccfc67c60502d299d16ea42527ed13","tid":2224858,"uid":49776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T01:05:38.000Z","msg":"【希望之聲2020年9月30日】（本台記者楊正綜合報導）<br />\n2020（第十六屆）北京車展9月26日-10月5日在北京中國國際展覽中心舉行。有視頻消息指，27日，一女子到吉利汽車展臺維權，被壯漢用黑布套頭擡走。昨天（29日）吉利集團副總裁楊學良通過微博作出迴應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/DynastyEndChaos/status/1310852060343083015\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDynastyEndChaos%2Fstatus%2F1310852060343083015&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyjFPTz8k007NAABMmnbcnzw%3D&h=79bfae44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDynastyEndChaos%2Fstatus%2F1310852060343083015&h=081efced\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/DynastyEndChaos/status/1310852060343083015</a><br />\n<br />\n視頻顯示，9月27日，吉利展臺上一女子哭訴&ldquo;你說你們敢買這輛車嗎？&rdquo;隨後被幾名安保人員用黑布軋蓋並擡走，期間女子不停呼喊&ldquo;放開我&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n有網友表示：<br />\n&ldquo;這和最近大量民房被開發商僱人強拆一樣，是一個重要的信號，說明政府統治黑社會化已經開始導致秩序失控&rdquo;。<br />\n&ldquo;這樣的行爲與舊時代山匪無異，把人裝麻袋裏，抗起就走&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n昨日下午，吉利集團副總裁楊學良通過微博迴應稱，此人並非維權人員，而是車展活動第三方運營公司招聘的禮儀接待人員，因爲工作分工調整導致情緒失常。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.soundofhope.org/post/427279?lang=b5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.soundofhope.org%2Fpost%2F427279%3Flang%3Db5&d=zLqexyjt4FDe6khRmo8kyjFPTz8k007NAABMmnbcnzw%3D&h=8abdfbe0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.soundofhope.org/post/427279?lang=b5</a>"},{"pid":"7bbfdacd8f7fdcc26beb0ecbe705e90d05cb8fc4","tid":2224858,"uid":49776,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T01:06:18.000Z","msg":"吉利汽車集團副總裁楊學良於9月30日在微博上作出澄清說，當事女子並非維權車主，而原本是吉利展台的一名禮儀人員。<br />\n<br />\n同時，他還貼出了一份署名為&ldquo;上海璽尊文化傳媒有限公司&rdquo;的致歉信。<br />\n<br />\n信中稱，該公司本為吉利品牌在北京車展期間提供運營服務，當事女子為該公司外聘禮儀人員。由於公司與該女子因工作問題產生矛盾，該女子情緒失控從後台跑至展台聲稱維權，並敲擊展車，抓傷現場的工作人員。<br />\n<br />\n為避免事態擴大，公司安保人員將其用黑布遮擋後帶至後場並報警。在屬地派出所的主持下，公司與該女子達成了和解。"},{"pid":"d2636b1aa6b2b745ffd383e716f71adc97bf2468","tid":2224858,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T01:13:28.000Z","msg":"可能滅左口<br />\n黑布抬走條屍<br />\n<br />\n等如強拆通常凌晨用機拆<br />\n就係想殺苦主防止苦主攪大"},{"pid":"ef96af25488f2f2dd14c9b63bfd9d87dfd18a09a","tid":2224858,"uid":104804,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T01:23:30.000Z","msg":"係支那好正常<br />\n有權有勢做咩都得<br />\n一陣比返錢公安就得<br />\n就算嘈到上微博好大件事<br />\n最後咩事都無<br />\n之前咩北京A8車牌個單都無事啦"},{"pid":"82ad45ec36b7a97b9a7b5fffbee6a8575d0c0871","tid":2224858,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2636b1aa6b2b745ffd383e716f71adc97bf2468","tid":2224858,"uid":26770,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T01:13:28.000Z","msg":"可能滅左口<br />\n黑布抬走條屍<br />\n<br />\n等如強拆通常凌晨用機拆<br />\n就係想殺苦主防止苦主攪大"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T01:26:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d230fb25a330e42307bd423dbf057feca14ef838","tid":2224858,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T01:57:25.000Z","msg":"中國遍地張獻忠"},{"pid":"07cca5b35ee94d12c05c36f8233bf451509c71c1","tid":2224858,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T02:14:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係中国特色"},{"pid":"cf4c52652e100e42c7a2bd12614ef8ac1aa060d6","tid":2224858,"uid":65747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T02:17:58.000Z","msg":"殺左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad778f65fe50a830c0c28369584195c928284ddf","tid":2224858,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep